parsed.explanation: Fixed the XML structure by removing a redundant closing </TITLE> tag that interrupted the bibliographic description. Corrected several encoding errors resulting from misinterpreted UTF-8 sequences (e.g., 'Gasse', 'Gespräch', 'Schottländischen', 'desgleichen', 'ohnlängst', 'müssen', and the symbol 'à').
